{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"@objc","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dynamic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"energySaveDetectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"set","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/energySaveDetectionRate","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"title":"energySaveDetectionRate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su"}],"symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"}],"externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration(py)energySaveDetectionRate","modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to 1, meaning that 1 frame per second is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 29 frames will be skipped, 1 frame is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: Usually you set a much lower value here as for the detectionRate property to save energy.","type":"text"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration/energySaveDetectionRate":{"title":"energySaveDetectionRate","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration\/energySaveDetectionRate","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"energySaveDetectionRate","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"UInt","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Su"}],"type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"energySaveDetectionRate","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The rate of detections\/recognitions per second in energy save mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Defaults to 1, meaning that 1 frame per second is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"When the video frame rate is 30, 29 frames will be skipped, 1 frame is detected\/recognized.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: if you set the detection rate greater to or equal to the video frame rate, no frames will be skipped,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the actual detection rate is limited by the video frame rate.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Note: Usually you set a much lower value here as for the detectionRate property to save energy.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration\/energysavedetectionrate"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"well as in energy saving mode.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"video frames per second.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:"}],"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"symbol"},"doc://net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK/documentation/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK":{"url":"\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk","type":"topic","title":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Version: 8.0.4","type":"text"}]}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"value":"occ","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage","op":"replace"},{"value":"Instance Property","path":"\/metadata\/roleHeading","op":"replace"},{"value":"energySaveDetectionRate","path":"\/metadata\/title","op":"replace"},{"value":"property","path":"\/metadata\/symbolKind","op":"replace"},{"value":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"energySaveDetectionRate"}],"path":"\/metadata\/fragments","op":"replace"},{"value":null,"path":"\/topicSections","op":"add"},{"value":null,"path":"\/relationshipsSections","op":"add"},{"value":null,"op":"add","path":"\/seeAlsoSections"},{"value":{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"NSUInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"energy